    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Round or roundish objects having the general shape of a sphere, which is a geometric shape comprising all points equidistant from the center. Balls may be of various materials and sizes, inflated, soft, or solid used in many different contexts and applications.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
